title: My Opinion on Vaccinations
description:
Take Dr. Berg's Advanced Evaluation Quiz: http://bit.ly/EvalQuiz

Your report will then be sent via email analyzing 104 potential symptoms, giving you a much deeper insight into your body issues. It's free and very enlightening. 

Dr. Berg talks about vaccinations. There are many toxins in vaccinations:
1. Msg
2. Anti-freeze
3. Formaldehyde
4. Aluminum
5. Lead
6. Acetone
7. Thiomersal
8. etc. etc.

I am not telling you to take vaccinations or not take them. Simply, look at the data from both sides and you decide. However, you need to get all the data - check out this research below.

RESEARCH:
http://vaccinepapers.org/high-mortali...
http://vaccinepapers.org/autism-broch...
http://vaccinepapers.org/debunking-al...
http://vaccinepapers.org/examine-evid...

The Vaccine industry is a 25 billion dollar business:
http://www.fiercepharma.com/special-r...
https://ccfvc.org/stuff/pdfs/Vaccine_...
https://www.cbsnews.com/news/supreme-...
http://www.nvic.org/NVIC-Vaccine-News...
http://ahrp.org/former-merck-scientis...
http://www.educate4theinjured.org/vac...

Dr. Eric Berg DC Bio:
Dr. Berg, 51 years of age is a chiropractor who specializes in weight loss through nutritional and natural methods. His private practice is located in Alexandria, Virginia. His clients include senior officials in the U.S. government and the Justice Department, ambassadors, medical doctors, high-level executives of prominent corporations, scientists, engineers, professors, and other clients from all walks of life. He is the author of The 7 Principles of Fat Burning, published by KB Publishing in January 2011. Dr. Berg trains chiropractors, physicians and allied healthcare practitioners in his methods, and to date he has trained over 2,500 healthcare professionals. He has been an active member of the Endocrinology Society, and has worked as a past part-time adjunct professor at Howard University.
